-- UniCredit Sells $636 Million of Hybrid Tier 1 Bonds Denominated in Euros
-- Tommaso Ebhardt
-- 2010-07-14T07:34:16Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-14/unicredit-sells-636-million-of-hybrid-tier-1-bonds-denominated-in-euros.html

          
          
             UniCredit SpA is selling 500 million
euros of hybrid Tier 1 bonds, it said in a statement distributed
by the Italian exchange.  
 UniCredit Corporate & Investment Banking, Credit Suisse
Group AG and JPMorgan Chase & Co are managing the sale, the
Italian bank said.  
          
          


  


        